title: Strako named to Summit League Player Watch List
text:
Strako named to Summit League Player Watch List
SIOUX FALLS, S.D. - Omaha men's golf junior Luke Strako was named to the 2024-25 Summit League Player Watch List, it was announced Thursday. An Omaha native, Strako led the Mavericks with a 73.4 stroke average during five fall events. He turned in a pair of top-10 finishes, including a season best runner-up finish at the Throw Down Up Top where he carded a 54-hole total of 215 (-4). Strako closed the fall slate with a t-10 finish at the ODU/Kilmaric Invitational, which included a season best round of 67 (-4). The Mavericks were selected ninth in the Coaches' Preseason...
